\begin_layout Standard
形式上解出方程组 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{j=1}^{n}a_{ij}x_{j}=b_{i}$
\end_inset

 的对角元：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{i}=\frac{1}{a_{ii}}\left(1-\sum_{j=1}^{i-1}a_{ij}x_{j}-\sum_{j=i+1}^{n}a_{ij}x_{j}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

